h3#pagination Pagination
.ch-g1-2
	.ch-leftcolumn
		h4 Demo
		iframe.mobile-demo(src="/mobile/demos/pagination", style="height:50px")
		a.more(href="/static/demos/mobile.html", target="_blank") See a complete demo
.ch-g1-2
	.ch-rightcolumn
		h4 Markup
		p
			| You can convert any list into a Pagination by adding the 
			code ch-pagination
			|  classname.
		p
			| To specify the current selected page, add the 
			code ch-pagination-current
			|  class to the list element.
		p
			| Be sure to add the 
			code type
			|  attribute to 
			strong previous
			|  and 
			strong next
			|  anchors reference, and set 
			code prev
			|  and 
			code next
			|  as value, this way:
		pre
			| <ul class="ch-pagination">
			| 	<li><a type="prev" href="#">Prev</a></li>
			| 	<li><a href="#">1</a></li>
			| 	<li class="ch-pagination-current"><a href="#">2</a></li>
			| 	<li><a href="#">3</a></li>
			| 	<li><a type="next" href="#">Next</a></li>
			| </ul>
.clearfix

